<span><span> </span></span></div><div><div><span><span>Baxter is focused on </span></span><span><span><span><span>saving</span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span>and</span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span>sustaining</span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span>lives</span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span>by</span></span></span></span><span><span> manufacturing high-quality products. </span></span><span><span><span><span>We</span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span>strive</span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span>to</span></span></span></span><span><span> create quality products for our customers each day. </span></span></div></div><div><div><span><span>Delivering life-saving products is about getting them right, and </span></span><span><span><span><span>attention</span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span>to</span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span>detail</span></span></span></span><span><span> is how we make sure we meet that challenge. We are a team that supports each other throughout each shift. Working together in a supportive and open </span></span><span><span><span><span>culture</span></span></span></span><span><span> makes our processes evolve for the better and engages our workforce. </span></span></div></div><div><div><span><span><span><span>You'll</span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span>be</span></span></span></span><span><span> offered extensive training, and the tight-knit working environment within t