/span><span><span><span><span>shift.</span></span></span></span></div></li><li><div><span><span>Normal visual acuity and the ability to distinguish color are </span></span><span><span><span><span>necessary.</span></span></span></span></div></li><li><div><span><span>Pass </span></span><span><span><span><span>the</span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span>Powered</span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span>Industrial</span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span>Truck</span></span></span></span><span><span> (</span></span><span><span><span><span>P.I.T.</span></span></span></span><span><span>) physical.</span></span></div></li><li><div><span><span>Stand, walk, climb stairs, reach forward, reach overhead, </span></span><span><span><span><span>balance,</span></span></span></span><span><span> stoop, crouch.</span></span></div></li><li><div><span><span>Handle objects and operate controls using fine/simple/firm grasping and fingering.</span></span></div></li></ul><div><div><span><span>We understand compensation is an important factor as you consider the next step in your career. </span></span><span><span><span><span>At</span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span>Baxter,</span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span>we</span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span>are</span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span>committed</span></span></span></span><span><span> to </span></span><span><span><span><span>equitable</span></span></span></span><span><span> pay for all our employees, and </span></span><span><span><span><span>we</span></span></span></span><span><span><span><sp